high_descs: from your starting direction move to the right side of the coffee table in front of you
pick up the keys off of the coffee table
turn left and walk over to the white chair left of the other white chair
place the keys down on the white chair
turn left and walk over to the black circle table to the left of the white chair
grab the keys off of the table
turn around and walk back over to the front of the white chair on your left
place the keys on the white chair
anns.task_desc: place two sets of keys down on the white chair

high_descs: Walk around the table and go to the side opposite the couch.
Pick up they keys on the table.
Turn left and walk to the chair.
Place the keys on the chair.
Step to the left.
Pick up the keys on the circular table.
Turn around and walk back to the chair.
Place the keys on the chair, to the right of the other keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on a chair.

high_descs: Go around the coffee table to face the other side of it.
Pick the keys up off of the coffee table.
Turn to the left to face the armchair.
Place the keys on top of the armchair.
Move to the left to face the side table.
Pick the keys up off of the side table.
Turn around and face the armchair to the left.
Place the keys next to the other set of keys on the armchair.
anns.task_desc: Place both sets of keys on top of the armchair.
